        "bio_paragraph_1": "<p>Thomas Sealey is a magic creator with a growing focus on everyday carry (EDC) design. His aim: to create objects designed to live naturally in the real world while quietly enabling moments of impossibility.</p>",
        "bio_paragraph_2": "<p>Drawn to the challenge of making magic feel unforced and organic, his work centres on adapting familiar, everyday objects so they can facilitate genuine magical moments without ever feeling like props. Over the past three years, Thomas has released eight professional products, each shaped by a consistent philosophy: practical design, reliable workmanship, and tools that working performers would genuinely want to carry and use.</p>",
